What is the output of the following code?

```java
public class NumberBox {
 public int value;
 public NumberBox(int value) {
 this.value = value;
 }
}

public class Main {
 public static void main(String[] args) {
 NumberBox box = new NumberBox(5);
 System.out.println("Before method call: " + box.value);
 doubleValue(box);
 System.out.println("After method call: " + box.value);
 }
 public static void doubleValue(NumberBox box) {
 box.value = box.value * 2;
 System.out.println("Inside method: " + box.value);
 }
}
```
